<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), url(https://images.pexels.com/photos/3768140/pexels-photo-3768140.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940);">
